overview: This is a clone of online tickets booking site (BookMyShow). BookMyShow is a ticketing application for movies, concerts, live events and much more. This clone is created using the react library as the front end.
BlockedIn is a chrome extension for blocking distracting websites and help users to manage their tasks effectively and increase their productivity. This project is implemented using Django.

Sudoku is an extremely popular logic and combinatorial math-based puzzle that millions attempt on a daily basis online and on paper. This project implements a Sudoku game in Python with an in-built automatic puzzle solver to add some Artificial Intelligence.

This is a clone of the popular notes taking site (Google Keep). Google Keep is an application that is used to store notes, add labels, archive and much more. This is implemented using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
This is an e-commerce website implemented using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
